{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5b52455933","title":"对《关于长沙、青岛、西安等地情况报告》的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"649b355daa","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":7,"articleId":"5b52455933"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"72504575ef","type":"title","text":"对《关于长沙、青岛、西安等地情况报告》的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"5b52455933"},{"id":"4ff3d3efee","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来、康生、伯达、江青等同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"5b52455933"},{"id":"da78328508","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请看一看，青岛、西安、长沙等地的情况是一样的，都是组织工农反学生，这样下去是不能解决问题的。似宜由中央发一指示，不准各地这样，然后写一篇社论，劝工农不要干预学生运动。北京就没有调动工农整学生，除人民大学曾调六百农民入城保郭影秋之外，其他都没有，以北京的经验告地方照办","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"5b52455933"},{"id":"597d7efffd","type":"paragraph","text":"我看谭启龙和这位副市长的意见是正确的。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"5b52455933"},{"id":"fa34022175","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"5b52455933"},{"id":"80f6965328","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年九月七日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"5b52455933"}],"page":{"id":"7154c80d1f","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"5b52455933","start":64,"end":64}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3eaa9b4dc2","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来、××、康生、伯达、×××、江青等同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"5b52455933"},{"id":"8c0f3e246b","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请看一看，青岛、西安、长沙等地的情况是一样的，都是组织工农反学生，这样下去是不能解决问题的。似宜由中央发一指示，不准各地这样，然后写一篇社论，劝工农不要干预学生运动。北京就没有调动工农整学生，除人民大学曾调六百农民入城保郭影秋之外，其他都没有，以北京的经验告地方照办。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"5b52455933"},{"id":"98469cdf39","type":"paragraph","text":"我看谭×××和这位副市长的意见是正确的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"5b52455933"},{"id":"b61175eaeb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"5b52455933"},{"id":"b7e854ded3","type":"subdate","text":"一九六七年九月七日","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"5b52455933"},{"id":"d019ee9bd8","type":"title","text":"对《关于长沙、青岛、西安等地情况报告》的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"5b52455933"}],"page":{"id":"df71372c0f","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"5b52455933","start":520,"end":520}}}},"__N_SSG":true}